To use this you need some stuff:
	gcc
	binutils
	grub (grub-legacy)
	mtools
	qemu (bochs coming soon)

if you get an error about cannot find /usr/lib/grub/i386-pc/...:
	Edit .config to point to wherever your grub stages are:
		Arch Linux: /usr/lib/grub/i386-pc

-OR-
	Use syslinux ;)

Getting started:
	Check out
		git clone git://gitorious.org/zombie/kernel.git
	Build
		make floppy
	Test
		make qemu
	Fix stuff ;)
	Submit
